- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with collecting and analyzing data about pins and user activity.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper discusses user interactions on a social network.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve natural language processing for analyzing comments on Pinterest.
